  "texts": [
    "Aqueous dispersions of PEDOT:PSS solution (>3%), ethylene glycol (99.8%), and Au nanoparticles (Au NPs) (~100 nm) dispersion in deionized water (DI) was purchased from Sigma-Aldrich.",
    "Acetone (99.5%) and isopropyl alcohol (IPA) (99.5%) were purchased from Samchun Chemical.",
    "An aqueous solution of PEDOT:PSS was firstly filtered through a 0.45 mm nylon syringe filter.",
    "Next, 5 wt% DMSO was added to the solution, and it was then mixed with 50 wt% IPA solvent by vigorously stirring at room temperature for half an hour.",
    "Subsequently, the base monomer and curing agent were mixed with a weight ratio of 10:1 at room temperature and then, placed into the vacuum desiccator to degas the PDMS mixture."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}